Package io.fluxcapacitor.common.api.search

Class GetDocumentResult

java.lang.Object
io.fluxcapacitor.common.api.search.GetDocumentResult
All Implemented Interfaces:
JsonType, RequestResult
public class GetDocumentResult extends Object implements RequestResult
Result returned in response to a GetDocument request.

This result includes a single SerializedDocument identified by its ID and collection, or null if the document could not be found.
